{"lastModified":1768915135243,"uri":"c::32018258056::vessel::c934f500-4b60-11f0-bc3d-0dc88f5784b1","yachtType":["Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nWelcome aboard the Hanse 460 Felice (2024)—a stunning 3-cabin sailing yacht designed for both luxury and performance. With its sleek lines and innovative design, the Hanse 460 Felice offers a perfect balance between comfort and speed, making it an ideal choice for both seasoned sailors and those new to the sport.\n \nThe Hanse 460 is celebrated for its spacious interior, offering unparalleled comfort with a modern aesthetic. The 3-cabin layout ensures privacy and ample space for up to six guests.\nEquipped with the latest sailing technologies, the Felice ensures a smooth and safe voyage, whether you’re cruising along the coast or exploring the open sea.\n\n \n\nThe Hanse 460 Felice is fully equipped with air conditioning, a generator, electric toilets, and a BBQ in the cockpit, ensuring a luxurious and comfortable experience at sea.\n \nThis yacht is not just about luxury—its performance-driven design makes it agile and responsive, perfect for those who love the thrill of sailing.\n \nWhether you’re planning a family vacation, a romantic getaway, or an adventurous sailing trip, we customise every charter to meet your specific needs.\n \nMarina Baotić is one of the most prestigious marinas in the Adriatic, offering easy access to some of the most beautiful sailing routes in Croatia.\n \nWith MK Yacht Explorer, you can expect top-tier service from a team of experienced professionals dedicated to making your charter experience unforgettable.\n \nSet sail on the Hanse 460 Felice with MK Yacht Explorer and experience the Adriatic like never before!","blueprint":{"name":"FELICE","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::c934f500-4b60-11f0-bc3d-0dc88f5784b1::assets::144fc3f0-4b64-11f0-b032-674cf5975b26/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::c934f500-4b60-11f0-bc3d-0dc88f5784b1::assets::142c3660-4b64-